{"meta":{"domain":"subjects","kid":"5077","authors":[{"fullname":"Nicolas Tournadre","id":"6"}],"title":"","dates":{"created_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:19 UTC","updated_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:19 UTC"}},"nodes":[{"index":0,"parent_index":-1,"body":"<p class=\"Paragraph\">Tibetan contains an important set of epistemic stative verbs (or copulas). These do not vary in relation to tense-aspect. As in the case of declarative stative verbs, a distinction is drawn between existential and essential copulas. The former are derived from the verb <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f61\u0f7c\u0f51\u0f0b<\/span> and the latter from the verb <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f61\u0f72\u0f53\u0f0b<\/span>.<\/p><p class=\"Paragraph\">The existential copulas and their negatives are:<\/p><table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"> <tbody> <tr> <td width=\"58\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f61\u0f7c\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f54\u0f0b\u0f60\u0f51\u0fb2\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"69\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f61\u0f7c\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f40\u0fb1\u0f72\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f7a\u0f51\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"70\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f61\u0f7c\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f66\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f7a\u0f51\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <\/tr> <tr> <td width=\"58\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f58\u0f7a\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f54\u0f0b\u0f60\u0f51\u0fb2\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"69\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f61\u0f7c\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f40\u0fb1\u0f72\u0f0b\u0f58\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f7a\u0f51\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"70\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f61\u0f7c\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f66\u0f0b\u0f58\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f7a\u0f51\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <\/tr> <\/tbody> <\/table><p class=\"Paragraph\">The essential copulas and their negatives are:<\/p><table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"> <tbody> <tr> <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f61\u0f72\u0f53\u0f0b\u0f54\u0f0b\u0f60\u0f51\u0fb2\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f61\u0f72\u0f53\u0f0b\u0f40\u0fb1\u0f72\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f7a\u0f51\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f61\u0f72\u0f53\u0f0b\u0f66\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f7a\u0f51\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <\/tr> <tr> <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f58\u0f72\u0f53\u0f0b\u0f54\u0f0b\u0f60\u0f51\u0fb2\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f61\u0f72\u0f53\u0f0b\u0f40\u0fb1\u0f72\u0f0b\u0f58\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f7a\u0f51\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f61\u0f72\u0f53\u0f0b\u0f66\u0f0b\u0f58\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f7a\u0f51\u0f0b<\/span><\/p> <\/td> <\/tr> <\/tbody> <\/table><p class=\"Paragraph\">These copulas express a high degree of probability and according to the context may be translated by the use of adverbs such as \u201csurely,\u201d \u201cprobably,\u201d or the modal verb \u201cmust.\u201d<\/p><ul> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f58\u0f72\u0f0b\u0f58\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f54\u0f7c\u0f0b\u0f61\u0f7c\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f54\u0f0b\u0f60\u0f51\u0fb2\u0f0d<\/span> \u201cThere must be a lot of people.\u201d<\/li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f60\u0f56\u0fb2\u0f7c\u0f42\u0f0b\u0f54\u0f0b\u0f61\u0f7c\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f40\u0fb1\u0f72\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f7a\u0f51\u0f0d<\/span> \u201cThere must be some nomads.\u201d<\/li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f41\u0f7c\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f92\u0fb1\u0f0b\u0f58\u0f72\u0f0b\u0f61\u0f72\u0f53\u0f0b\u0f42\u0fb1\u0f72\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f7a\u0f51\u0f0d<\/span> \u201cHe must be Chinese.\u201d<\/li> <\/ul><p class=\"Paragraph\">There is a slight difference between the auxiliaries formed with <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f60\u0f51\u0fb2\u0f0b<\/span> and those formed with <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f62\u0f7a\u0f51\u0f0b<\/span>. The former suggests that the speaker\u2019s inference is based on his direct observation of the evidence, while the latter indicates that the speaker\u2019s inference is based on logic or on factual information not borne out by observation.<\/p>","title":""}]}